com.google.cloud.datastore

Interface ValueBuilder<V,P extends Value<V>,B extends ValueBuilder<V,P,B>>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the data type that the Value object holds.
    P - the value type.
    B - the value type's associated builder.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlobValue.Builder, BooleanValue.Builder, DateTimeValue.Builder, DoubleValue.Builder, EntityValue.Builder, KeyValue.Builder, LatLngValue.Builder, ListValue.Builder, LongValue.Builder, NullValue.Builder, RawValue.Builder, StringValue.Builder

    public interface ValueBuilder<V,P extends Value<V>,B extends ValueBuilder<V,P,B>>
    A common interface for Value builders.
